  "body": "Is this a bug report or feature request?\r\n* Feature Request\r\n\r\n**Feature Request**\r\n\r\nAre there any similar features already existing: The Ceph operator performs orchestration for Ceph distributed storage, which has similar concepts for deploying cloud-native storage in kubernetes.\r\n\r\nWhat should the feature do:  This feature would introduce new CRD types for Minio and an operator that performs the deployment, orchestration, and management of Minio in Kubernetes.",
